{"tid":1856733,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]平時網速極快，一開線上game跌到得8Mbps(down)0.15Mbps(up)","createTime":"2020-02-01T18:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T12:45:08.000Z","uid":345946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fbbbd8507e3ede9c6e945edd4fc063373b1c04b","tid":1856733,"uid":345946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:45:47.000Z","msg":"求救，我最近轉咗快HKBN plan, 1000M。因為舊router上限得300M所以買咗新router Tp-link Archer AX10。<br />\n以下為正常網速，有speedtest同ofca<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTt30P3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTt30P3.png&h=ef6ad5ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFSz7u4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFSz7u4.png&h=ec3ba378&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n原本好地地咩事都冇，有日突然打機時手賤check speedtest就發現咗跌到得...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTRUn3p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTRUn3p.png&h=3e9be457&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7Gw9Jq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7Gw9Jq.png&h=090bade8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n利申，所有線上game如：R6,CSGO,LoL,Apex(淨開客戶端origin都係)，都係仆街。但係只要唔開聯網就跑到上800Mbps。<br />\n咁小弟我就上網睇睇發生咩事會咁啦，明明轉plan前電腦一直都冇事。所以連網卡都update咗去最新驅動，連modem連由師傅換咗個新嘅。奇怪嘅係，電腦一跌，小弟家中其他裝備都仲係上到300Mbps(圖為小弟嘅poco f1手機)<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/624458284270878734/673235767841128468/Screenshot_2020-02-02-02-38-20-020_org.zwanoo.android.speedtest.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F624458284270878734%2F673235767841128468%2FScreenshot_2020-02-02-02-38-20-020_org.zwanoo.android.speedtest.jpg&h=ef1299e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電腦型號：Lenovo Legion Y740 17&quot; (81HH000FHH)<br />\n(17.3吋Full HD / i7-8750H / 32GB DDR4 RAM / 512 GB SSD + 1 TB HDD / NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2080 8GB)<br />\n有冇Ching幫到小弟，跪求搭救"},{"pid":"33b1f75511e89927ea595a40abc599919cd2c1e0","tid":1856733,"uid":61953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T20:33:13.000Z","msg":"開左QoS"},{"pid":"68bf658507cd67c889a2d68598607c1749ad79cf","tid":1856733,"uid":345946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b1f75511e89927ea595a40abc599919cd2c1e0","tid":1856733,"uid":61953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T20:33:13.000Z","msg":"開左QoS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"小弟我試過啦，用tether無論set 電腦係高優先度定熄QoS都係咁"},{"pid":"f193499c6463b7c46467c0795246486e79277178","tid":1856733,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"用TP-link仲夠膽上連登講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e093500dc8c6dc40b2913296ab51638b389876","tid":1856733,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"Tp-link <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd04d8b12fdd1ecc9e174788eb3df489a2b4ed4f","tid":1856733,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"直插HKBN 隻垃圾 Router 試下?"},{"pid":"021513a6f7917f82a0bd33c04d7e09699032b539","tid":1856733,"uid":345946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f193499c6463b7c46467c0795246486e79277178","tid":1856733,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"用TP-link仲夠膽上連登講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"用TP-link有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f1790e67237a7c232cb820467c92eaca6ef8b8",